WEBVTT

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:06.600
Good morning, family. I am outside. We had high winds here in Oklahoma today. I'm talking about

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:15.400
strong, very unusual winds. This little guy, this little squirrel, was up in a tree

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:19.160
and he got blown out. I don't know where his mama went, but he's lying out here on the ground. Unfortunately,

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:27.560
his sister died in the fall. I just love nature and

00:00:27.560 --> 00:00:33.040
I couldn't stand to see him there just die. I've never touched a squirrel before

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:39.720
that was alive; only the ones that we ate. Grandpa would always eat squirrel and cook it up in the

00:00:39.720 --> 00:00:47.360
frying pan as a boy and make squirrel stew. But this is a little squirrel, and

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:53.640
I love God's creatures. We found him some milk

00:00:53.640 --> 00:01:00.040
and stuff to try to keep him alive. I told my daughter, 'If we can keep him alive and

00:01:00.040 --> 00:01:05.000
feed him like the lady on the YouTube channel who feeds all the nuts to the squirrels, I'll

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:10.400
film him all the time for you all and put it on here.'I know our content might get boring; I try

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:16.120
not to say the same thing over and over, but that's what's inside of me. I

00:01:16.120 --> 00:01:22.800
told my son, 'I don't want to make boring content; I want it to be inspiring and to

00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:29.440
lift you up.'I just know that God is no respecter of persons, and what

00:01:29.440 --> 00:01:35.120
He did for us, He'll do for you. We're a work in progress just like

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:40.520
everybody else, but I know that people try to put us on a pedestal.

00:01:40.520 --> 00:01:45.440
I'm just telling you, we're just like you; we're believing

00:01:45.440 --> 00:01:51.680
for everyday miracles and for the supernatural in our lives. I

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:57.400
wake up every day with an anticipation that God's going to show up and do something mighty in our lives.

00:01:57.400 --> 00:02:05.480
I told you all I was driving around and the Lord told me great favor was coming on His

00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:14.640
bride, on His church—that we would see the greatest favor, the greatest impartation of favor on us. As

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:20.960
we walk into the grocery stores, we would walk in favor like

00:02:20.960 --> 00:02:27.080
you wouldn't believe. I believe it's time now for exceedingly abundantly above all that we

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:34.280
dare ask or think as we enter into the rest this year that God said He was going to

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:41.120
do something mighty inside of us. I was

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:45.920
praying over Israel and what

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:52.120
He said about when we walk into churches, that there would be great deliverances for people that are

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:59.000
walking in bondage from all kinds of addictions, torments,

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:04.600
depression, and anxiety. He doesn't want

00:03:04.600 --> 00:03:09.040
anything

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:15.040
missing out of your life; He wants you to be made whole. It's

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:21.200
not for us to live a busted and disgusted life, but to live a supernatural life. Just

00:03:21.200 --> 00:03:27.520
like Peter, there's stages of glory. The Lord showed me

00:03:27.520 --> 00:03:32.000
it's like first starting out with a

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:39.360
single-shot.22.

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:45.080
